\newlabel{tab:hccp_logreg}{{14}{26}{HCCP applied on $(\phat _{\mathrm {LogReg}}, \shat )$ vs.\ on $(\phat _{\mathrm {GBM}}, \shat )$. The $\shat $-bin gap and minority-class coverage are essentially unchanged across the base-predictor swap, confirming the conformal-side gain is decoupled from the AUPRC gain}{table.14}{}}
